  "detailed_description": "<h1>Workshop</h1><p>Please check out the Workshop for more levels with fancy images!</p><br><h1>Follow me!</h1><p>Discord：<br>Twitter：Fish Chain Games</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦Easy to operate and fun to play✦</h2>Drag the mouse to shoot the ball, hit and destroy the bricks!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470290/extras/143c38f258fcbc089813aed648025033.poster.avif?t=1688140617\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470290/extras/143c38f258fcbc089813aed648025033.webm?t=1688140617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470290/extras/143c38f258fcbc089813aed648025033.mp4?t=1688140617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦Easy yet strategic✦</h2>Different bricks have different effects. Use the best strategy, or you may be into trouble.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦Multiple game modes✦</h2> • Story mode: experience the authentic story performing a brick exorcist<br><br> • Endless mode: experience the fun of breaking bricks in randomly generated levels<br> • Edit mode: create your own level, share to the world through Workshop<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦Multiple choices and endings✦</h2>Make different choices, experience different plots. Different endings are waiting to be revealed, including the hidden ending!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦Easy to use editor✦</h2>The built-in editor is easy to use, and you can create interesting levels with a few clicks of the mouse. Upload to the workshop and share your levels with everyone!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470290/extras/9055845c1ef5678c1403855aa8d3efe1.poster.avif?t=1688140617\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470290/extras/9055845c1ef5678c1403855aa8d3efe1.webm?t=1688140617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470290/extras/9055845c1ef5678c1403855aa8d3efe1.mp4?t=1688140617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
